curam.util.ctm.bom.resources.impl

Class AppResourceDependentBOMImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.ctm.bom.BusinessObjectModuleImpl
      • curam.util.ctm.bom.resources.impl.AppResourceDependentBOMImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BusinessObjectModule, DependentBOM
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CSSAppResourceDependentBOMImpl, ImageAppResourceDependentBOMImpl, PropertiesAppResourceDependentBOMImpl, SchemaAppResourceDependentBOMImpl, XMLAppResourceDependentBOMImpl

    public abstract class AppResourceDependentBOMImpl
extends BusinessObjectModuleImpl
implements DependentBOM
    This is the Dependent Business Object Module implementation for an AppResource BOM. A resource BOM consists of the resource in the specified locale, or any locale if none is specified. This class is responsible for retrieving information on the BOMs that an AppResource BOM is dependent on.
